<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.uni-muenster.de/UrFruehGeschichte/kier1.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.uni-muenster.de/UrFruehGeschichte/kier1.htm" rel="nofollow">Archaeological Investigations on the Beginning of Blast Furnace-Technology in Central Europe</a></li>
