<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> Andrea Matthies: Medieval Treadwheels. Artists' Views of Building Construction, <i>Technology and Culture</i>, Vol. 33, No. 3 (Jul., 1992), p.515</li>
