<li>White, Lynn, Jr. <i>Medieval technology and social change.</i> Oxford: Clarendon Press, 1962.</li>
<li>White, Lynn, Jr., "The Study of Medieval Technology, 1924-1974: Personal Reflections" <i>Technology and Culture</i> <b>16</b>.4 (October 1975), pp. 519-530. A chronology and basic bibliography of landmark studies.</li>
</ul>
